Name: BattleBots
Title: World Championship VII -- Round of 32 (Part 1 of 2)
Desc: The first half of the Round of 32 will see eight battles -- winners progress to the Round of 16.
LongDescription: The world championship kicks off with the best combat robots in the world competing for the ultimate prize: the Giant Nut; the first half of the Round of 32 will see eight do-or-die battles -- winners progress to the Round of 16.
